        "Dear Sir,",
        "I am writing this letter to express my dissatisfaction with an evening course which is being delivered in the school premises.",
        "Actually, Sir, a seminar was conducted in the school campus to enhance awareness among the students regarding the extra-curricular activities, such as cooking.I took participation in a course of South Indian cooking.Because I urge to learn the art of their cookery skills.",
